Class ChooseStructureElementPropertyDescriptor

java.lang.Object
  java.beans.FeatureDescriptor
      java.beans.PropertyDescriptor
          de.hu.gralog.beans.propertydescriptor.ChooseStructureElementPropertyDescriptor

public class ChooseStructureElementPropertyDescriptor
extends PropertyDescriptor

This class is a special PropertyDescriptor that can be used to define properties for algorithms, structures, vertices and edges in GrALoG. This PropertyDescriptor allows the user to choose an element ( an element is either a vertex or an edge ) of the currently active structure. The elements that the user is allowed to choose from can be specified by a StructureElementFilter. Make sure that the property corresponding to this descriptor has a type compatible to all elements you allow the user to choose from.

Author:
ordyniak
